Shift + ! + Enter ------> To create the boilor plate of HTML at VS Code editor.
(Boilor Plate is the pre set blueprint of the HTML)

To create HTML file ------> index.html
To create CSS file ------> style.css
To create JavaScript file ------> script.js

To Connect CSS file with HTML file -------> 2 ways to connect
                                            (a) Directly write the code in HTML file inside <head> tag by using <style> tag
                                            (b) By linking the external style.css file by using 
                                                  (i) If the css file inside the same project folder
                                                        <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "./style.css" >
                                                        
                                                        or
                                                        
                                                        link:css + enter   ------- this will convert to <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "style.css" >
                                                        
                                                   (ii) If the css file outside the same project folder
                                                        <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "../style.css" >
                                                        
                                         
                                                        
                                                        
To Connect JavaScript file with HTML file -------> 2 ways to connect
                                            (a) Directly write the code in HTML file inside <head> tag's inside the <script></script> tag
                                            (b) By linking the external script.js file by using 
                                                         
                                                        
                                                                                                           
.container + Enter ----> This will create one div tag with having class name container at VS code editor                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
                                                        
